r></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.geoip-db-filename-examples">   <h3 class="title">范例</h3>   <span>    <div class="example" id="example-4485">     <p><strong>Example #1 <span class="function"><strong style="color:#CC7832">geoip_db_filename()</strong></span>函数的使用范例：</strong></p>     <div class="example-contents"><p>     如下代码将会打印数据库相对应的文件名。     </p></div>     <div class="example-contents"> <div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"> <span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br /><br /></span><span style="color: #007700">print&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">geoip_db_filename</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">GEOIP_COUNTRY_EDITION</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /><br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span> </span> </span></div>     </div>      <div class="example-contents"><p>以上例程会输出：</p></div>     <div class="example-contents screen" style="background:black;padding-left:5px;"> <div class="cdata"><span> /usr/share/GeoIP/GeoIP.dat </span></div>     </div>    </div>   </span>  </div>     <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.geoip.php">GeoIP 函数</a></div></div>
